8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 7=

11
00:00:42,399 --> 00:00:45,479
Your Highness.
Please spare that assassin's life.

12
00:00:48,039 --> 00:00:49,280
He's my brother.

13
00:00:57,799 --> 00:00:59,560
So you took that blade for me

14
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:01,880
just for his sake?

15
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:11,120
Your Highness.

16
00:01:14,120 --> 00:01:15,000
That assassin,

17
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:17,120
I'll deal with him myself.

18
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:19,280
You should have some rest.

19
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,359
Confess everything!

20
00:01:29,719 --> 00:01:30,760
Why did you try to kill His Highness?

21
00:01:30,959 --> 00:01:31,599
Speak!

22
00:01:34,599 --> 00:01:35,719
Where's Shiqi?

23
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,359
Shiqi?

24
00:01:41,719 --> 00:01:43,599
Such intimacy.

25
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:45,280
She's my sister.

26
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:46,840
Murong Jinghe,

27
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:49,920
everything was my plan.

28
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,959
It has nothing to do with her.

29
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:54,400
If you want to kill or torture someone,

30
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,680
come at me.

31
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,319
Jian!

32
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,760
Your Highness, please spare him.

33
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:05,599
Shiqi!

34
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,439
He must have thought

35
00:02:07,439 --> 00:02:09,000
you had killed me,

36
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,639
so he attacked you.

37
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,199
Please spare him, Your Highness!

38
00:02:14,319 --> 00:02:16,560
You're pleading for him?

39
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:24,800
Interesting.

40
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,599
Mei Lin,

41
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,280
since you joined my career,

42
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,240
you seem submissive,

43
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:32,800
yet you always hold on to your pride.

44
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:41,039
Turns out you can actually soften up.

45
00:02:43,599 --> 00:02:45,960
And now you're crying, begging me

46
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:47,599
for another man.

47
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,240
Murong Jinghe!

48
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:52,840
Come at me if you dare!

49
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,039
Jian...

50
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:57,240
Such deep affection between you two.

51
00:02:58,719 --> 00:02:59,759
How entertaining.

52
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,199
Your Highness,

53
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:04,240
he's also a top killer
of the Shadow Bureau.

54
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:07,360
He could serve you well in the palace.

55
00:03:08,439 --> 00:03:09,800
If I don't spare him,

56
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,120
will you hate me?

57
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,000
I could spare him,

58
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:32,759
but all men in the palace
must be eunuchs.

59
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,639
Your Highness...

60
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:39,479
I already am one.

61
00:03:50,159 --> 00:03:51,199
(Once you're avenged,)

62
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,759
(let's leave the Shadow Bureau)

63
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,759
(and live in seclusion,
what do you say?)

64
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:57,120
(Sounds great. Deal then.)

65
00:04:04,159 --> 00:04:04,960
(Shiqi,)

66
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,840
(Murong Jinghe caused your death.)

67
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:13,199
(I'll get into the palace and kill him.)

68
00:04:13,340 --> 00:04:15,000
(Shiqi)

69
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:16,079
(Shiqi)
(I'll avenge you.)

70
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:28,959
Jian,

71
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,600
you were so silly.

72
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,360
Enough.

73
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,199
Come here.

74
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:03,079
Shiqi.

75
00:05:03,360 --> 00:05:04,160
Shiqi!

76
00:05:10,639 --> 00:05:12,000
You want to save him, don't you?

77
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:14,519
Fine.

78
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:17,199
I'll give you three days.

79
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:20,360
Get the cure for the Bone-Erosion Powder
from Murong Xuanlie

80
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,720
and heal my legs.

81
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,040
Then I'll spare his life.

82
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,560
Otherwise,

83
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,759
you and your dear brother

84
00:05:26,959 --> 00:05:28,279
will go to hell together.

85
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,040
Alright.

86
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,560
Jian,

87
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,839
I'll find the antidote.

88
00:05:44,839 --> 00:05:45,680
You should leave.

89
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,279
Shiqi,

90
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,519
I'm not leaving.

91
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:50,639
I won't leave you in danger alone.

92
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:53,399
The reason I stayed in the palace

93
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,319
is that I smelled the same scent

94
00:05:55,399 --> 00:05:57,120
on Murong Xuanlie as well.

95
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,800
I've been investigating him in secret.

96
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,639
He is highly suspicious.

97
00:06:02,040 --> 00:06:04,480
There is a hidden chamber in his study.

98
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,560
I couldn't get inside.

99
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,800
Maybe another time, I can.

100
00:06:08,319 --> 00:06:10,639
If there's proof he's the head
of the Shadow Bureau,

101
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,519
I'll kill him myself.

102
00:06:14,399 --> 00:06:15,639
This revenge is mine to take.

103
00:06:15,959 --> 00:06:17,399
I don't want you involved.

104
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,839
Shiqi,

105
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,480
you see me as a brother.

106
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:21,959
How could I abandon you

107
00:06:21,959 --> 00:06:22,959
at a moment like this?

108
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,160
Let me stay with you.

109
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:29,120
Please.

110
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,399
Jian...

111
00:06:41,399 --> 00:06:42,199
It's alright.

112
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,319
I've got you.

113
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:54,759
So, do you have a plan now?

114
00:06:56,319 --> 00:06:58,759
I need to finish the task
Murong Jinghe gave me

115
00:06:59,079 --> 00:07:00,560
before I can help you escape.

116
00:07:03,920 --> 00:07:05,560
Your Highness, Princess Anhe is here.

117
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:11,040
Aren't you deeply in love
with that loser?

118
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:13,120
You even gave up your life

119
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,959
to protect him.

120
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:16,240
Why bother to come to me today?

121
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:21,879
Your Highness already has General Muye
and her troops.

122
00:07:22,279 --> 00:07:23,680
An orphan girl like me

123
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:26,759
is not even worthy of being your shadow.

124
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:30,639
All I could do was risk my life
for a protector.

125
00:07:30,839 --> 00:07:32,480
Are you blaming me for being heartless?

126
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:39,519
Mei Lin,

127
00:07:39,800 --> 00:07:40,600
are you alright?

128
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:41,959
Your Highness,

129
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,680
Princess Anhe
went to see Prince Xuanlie.

130
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:46,040
She took poisoned wine herself.

131
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,759
She poisoned herself?

132
00:08:05,540 --> 00:08:07,500
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

