155
00:09:20,340 --> 00:09:22,580
ظآزHow beautifulظآز

156
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:26,940
ظآزTwo hearts leaning into one anotherظآز

157
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:30,460
ظآزPerfectly, impossibly rightظآز
